Sierra Leone Western Area Administrative Boundaries

Source: R/zzz.R
sf_sle.Rd

A list of length 2 containing geographic administrative boundary data for Sierra Leone, stored as simple features (sf) objects.

Usage

sf_sle

Format

named list of sf objects

Details

Each admin level can be joined to the example df_ll_ebola dataset with a join by specification of c("pcode" = "adm3_pcode") and c("pcode" = "adm4_pcode") respectively. These should be passed as the join_by field in each geo_data specification passed to place_ui and place_server.

Examples

sf_sle$adm1
#> NULL
sf_sle$adm2
#> NULL
